# ── Notion ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Database already created: "🚀 AutoDeal — Leads" in your Life OS
# Database ID is hardcoded in the API route — no env var needed for it.
#
# You still need an Integration Token so the website can write to it:
#   1. Go to https://www.notion.so/my-integrations
#   2. Click "New integration" → name it "AutoDeal Website" → Submit
#   3. Copy the "Internal Integration Secret" below
#   4. Open the "🚀 AutoDeal — Leads" database in Notion
#   5. Click "..." (top right) → "Connections" → add "AutoDeal Website"
NOTION_TOKEN=secret_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ── Google Sheets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No service account needed — uses a simple Apps Script webhook.
#
#   1. Create a new Google Sheet (name it "AutoDeal Leads")
#   2. Extensions → Apps Script
#   3. Delete existing code, paste the contents of google-apps-script.js
#   4. Deploy → New deployment → Type: Web app
#      Execute as: Me | Who has access: Anyone
#   5. Copy the Web App URL and paste below
GOOGLE_SHEETS_WEBHOOK_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/YOUR_SCRIPT_ID/exec
